    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sound E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 inline-six powerplant. This unit maintains excellent compression across all cylinders, and the dual-VANOS system has been recently overhauled to ensure precise variable valve timing. The chassis incorporates reinforced rear subframe mounts, proactively addressing the platform's known structural vulnerabilities. Power is channeled through a 6-speed manual transmission to a factory-spec limited-slip differential. While the finish exhibits minor road patina, the handling dynamics are sharp, aided by refreshed suspension bushings and Bilstein dampers. This is a driver-oriented specimen optimized for longitudinal and lateral performance.",
      "price": 32500.0,
